open-course-player

open-course-player 是一个面向本地课程目录和媒体目录的开源桌面播放器。

项目计划使用 Tauri、Vue、Element Plus、mpegts.js、hls.js，以及 mpv/FFmpeg
相关播放组件。第三方声明统一维护在 THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md。

发布二进制时必须保留所有必要的第三方许可证和署名声明。

---

English:

open-course-player is an open source desktop player for local course folders and
media libraries.

The project plans to use Tauri, Vue, Element Plus, mpegts.js, hls.js, and
mpv/FFmpeg related playback components. Third-party notices are maintained in
THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.

Binary releases must preserve all required third-party license and attribution
notices.
